{"tid":2233732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聶德權：公務員私人朋友之間亦需謹言，流出可構成影響違反公務員規例。","createTime":"2020-10-07T10:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T06:26:08.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":103,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"b22430e7bb2bea1b431092dfa94647d2d71d2416","tid":2233732,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:50:46.000Z","msg":"過咗幾個禮拜都冇人講過呢一點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/36348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F36348&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=5de44f16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F36348&h=0bd7740b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/36348</a><br />\n<br />\n【有線新聞】公務員事務局局長聶德權表示，下月起會要求新入職的公務員簽署文件，確認擁護《基本法》及效忠香港特區。他又指公務員在網上私人平台發表言論，如果被公開了引起質疑，政府也會審視有否違規。<br />\n<br />\n七月後入職公務員要簽署文件確認擁護《基本法》及效忠香港特區，政府亦正研究如何推展到現職公務員。公務員事務局局長聶德權：「對於新入職的公務員，這是一個聘用條件，正與律政司進行相關工夫，確定如果現職公務員不簽署誓言，到底跟進行動怎樣。」<br />\n<br />\n他指國安法第六條列明就任公職的宣誓要求，第35條就列明「違反誓言會即時喪失職務」。<span class=\"red\">他提醒公務員在網上也要慎言，聶德權：「朋友之間傾談或表達一些看法，你用了私人渠道或社交平台，本來設定是私人的。但在現今社會，有可能你以為私人平台突然被公開，雖然本身未必是你的原意，信息公開後，所產生的影響亦可能構成影響，招致一些質疑時，我們會小心看看有否違反公務員相關規例。」</span><br />\n<br />\n高級公務員協會主席李方冲認為，當局應清晰交代「擁護基本法」的定義。李方冲：「甚麼叫不擁護、甚麼叫違反規例，我們暫時不太清楚。大部分人不太抗拒簽，有些快要退休不想簽怎樣做，仍未處理。」他希望政府尊重公務員的言論自由，如在社交平台發表的言論被質疑，應有申訴機制。"},{"pid":"c37daa73755fde3358874a6571e4ff7e1f600fb6","tid":2233732,"uid":224533,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:53:18.000Z","msg":"公務員發開口夢也要小心點"},{"pid":"e5d9bfa42ad173a1d2ef015a106aa08ccfdb4c8b","tid":2233732,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:54:00.000Z","msg":"賣身入共家？"},{"pid":"4d340c4a8adae9ff2a8f39d0f145c531948cc080","tid":2233732,"uid":122,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:54:52.000Z","msg":"公務員 教師 下個到社工註冊局"},{"pid":"81058bbfcdcb4188b26f7edb07efc5a075ca9013","tid":2233732,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:55:20.000Z","msg":"想返工都唔得<br />\n迫香港人上絕路"},{"pid":"0228c771f11fd58f791a407bf1ec9f6ff38e41f5","tid":2233732,"uid":108606,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:55:37.000Z","msg":"學藍消防曱甴處長講句：個人感受抒發囉"},{"pid":"b196849210c91df3980f84b87ddcac9ef6c0523c","tid":2233732,"uid":272565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"講都唔講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce525dfcc8870d7ac2b9e1f066b1862d1dad709","tid":2233732,"uid":200280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"入去預咗一世番唔出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f398d348558d118c90c06bc75bd9fb45286e0ed8","tid":2233732,"uid":256059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:55:58.000Z","msg":"又係文革手段"},{"pid":"68f04f0fe9a7ed44aae93a2f57126305fcc43488","tid":2233732,"uid":26168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"鼓勵篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76770a637c1e0c200d2651d618aa13837fc1828","tid":2233732,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:57:08.000Z","msg":"奶共狗"},{"pid":"6519e5794f485f920a54563b421f12da535a66d1","tid":2233732,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:57:18.000Z","msg":"琴日阿楊狗話大學講港獨話題冇問題架喎 <br />\n小學生先唔岩討論"},{"pid":"9e71c11cb1b6f77ba4e13a83ca077f904b91df8f","tid":2233732,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi